Security Notice from SOE
</font>
</td>
<TD valign=top>
<FONT SIZE="1" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
<IMG SRC="http://boards.station.sony.com/everquest/posticonnew.gif"  BORDER=0 ALT="New Announcement!"> posted by ubbadmin&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<FONT SIZE="1" FACE="Verdana, Arial" COLOR="#00ffff">(01-01-1999 through 12-31-2001)</FONT><HR>
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Security Notice:<P>All members should beware of scams that ask for your credit card information or password via an e-mail or other communication -- Sony Online Entertainment and Verant Interactive will never ask for our members’ personal information via an e-mail.  And members should be careful not to download viruses or harmful programs from the Internet that may allow hackers access to their systems.  If you believe you have fallen for a scam and given out your personal information or someone has contacted you via an e-mail requesting your personal information, change your password right away and notify us at <a href="mailto:techsupport@station.sony.com ">privacy@station.sony.com </a>.  To change your password, go to your Membership Info area <a href="http://www.station.sony.com/services/accountinfo.jhtml"> www.station.sony.com/services/accountinfo.jhtml </a></FONT>
</FONT>
